About the Company
Our Client is a packaging materials company specialising in the research and production of environmentally sustainable materials for the packaging industry.
Responsibilities
We’re looking for a driven Sales Manager with a proven track record in sales and business development within the food packaging industry to build the company’s outreach within the region.

  Develop new business opportunities for the company’s products and services within the region;
  Build a healthy sales pipeline by constantly generating leads and servicing potential clients;
  Meet with potential client stakeholders to build brand awareness and business networks;
  Conduct sales pitches and presentations to potential clients;
  Overcome objections with good product or technical understanding;
  Perform negotiations and price discussions as necessary;
  Gather industry information to plan sales strategy;
  Plan and oversee activities of field sales executives to grow sales within the assigned region.

Requirements

  Diploma or Degree in Materials Engineering would be an advantage;
  At least 3 to 5 years of technical sales experience within the packaging and materials industry;
  Good understanding of the coating and materials industry, particularly within the food packaging sector would be an advantage;
  Excellent client relationship management skills;
  Strong interpersonal, negotiation and persuasion skills;
  Confident, go-getting personality, comfortable communicating with decision-makers;
  Resilience, determination and action-orientation;
  Good leadership skills;
  Good communication skills, both written and spoken.

Employment Details

  Based in Singapore;
  Attractive base salary with commissions.

